import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data.groupby('site').mean().reset_index()
    plt.bar(data['site'], data['yield'])
    plt.axhline(y=data['yield'].mean(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Mean Yield')
    plt.legend()
    plt.xticks(rotation=45, ha='right')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data[['yield', 'variety']]
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.boxplot([data[data['variety'] == variety]['yield'] for variety in data['variety'].unique()], 
               labels=data['variety'].unique())
    ax.set_xlabel('Variety')
    ax.set_ylabel('Yield')
    ax.set_title('How does the yield vary by variety?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['year'])]
    data = data.sort_values(by='year')
    plt.plot(data['year'], data['yield'], color='blue')
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('Yield')
    plt.title('What is the trend of yield over the years?')
    plt.grid(True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='yield', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['yield'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label=f"Mean: {data['yield'].mean():0.2f}")
    plt.axvline(data['yield'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label=f"Median: {data['yield'].median():0.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of yield across all sites?')
    plt.xlabel('Yield')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data_pivot = data.pivot(index='variety', columns='site', values='yield')
    ax = sns.heatmap(data_pivot, cmap='YlGnBu', annot=True, fmt='.2f', cbar_kws={'label': 'Yield'})
    ax.set_xlabel('Site')
    ax.set_ylabel('Variety')
    ax.set_title('How does the yield vary by site and variety?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
